32:07.884 --> 32:09.635
But Laura talked me into it.

32:13.139 --> 32:16.350
We were going to the Roadhouse
to meet boys.

32:17.769 --> 32:19.645
Their names are

32:20.647 --> 32:26.068
Josh, Rick and Tim.

32:28.613 --> 32:31.198
They're about 20 years old.

32:33.826 --> 32:35.953
And they're nice to us.

32:48.007 --> 32:49.925
And they make us feel
like we're older.

32:54.389 --> 32:57.099
Rick asks if we wanna go party.

32:57.475 --> 32:59.726
And Laura says, yes.

33:00.395 --> 33:05.190
And all of a sudden, I feel this knot
building up in my stomach.

33:05.400 --> 33:09.736
But when Laura gets in the truck
with Rick, I go anyway.

33:11.572 --> 33:13.907
Stream in the woods.

33:15.368 --> 33:16.702
Full moon, I think.

33:17.328 --> 33:19.538
It's pale and light out.

33:23.584 --> 33:27.254
Laura starts to dance
around the boys.

33:32.301 --> 33:35.137
She begins to move her hips...

33:35.805 --> 33:40.267
...back and forth.

33:43.438 --> 33:48.150
Rick starts to clap, but Tim doesn't
do anything, he just watches.

33:50.153 --> 33:52.612
Somehow, that makes me angry.

33:53.614 --> 33:56.408
So I say, "Let's go skinny-dipping."

34:01.789 --> 34:04.249
We take off our clothes.

34:06.586 --> 34:08.336
I know the boys are watching.

34:09.130 --> 34:12.090
Laura starts to kiss Josh and Rick.

34:12.967 --> 34:14.551
I don't know what to do.

34:15.887 --> 34:18.138
So I swim away.

34:21.434 --> 34:24.186
I feel like I wanna run, but I don't.

34:27.565 --> 34:29.983
Tim swims out to me.

34:33.279 --> 34:35.489
He kisses my hand...

34:37.742 --> 34:39.534
...and then me.

34:46.793 --> 34:49.503
I can still feel that kiss.

34:52.006 --> 34:56.093
His lips are warm and sweet.

34:58.930 --> 35:01.098
My heart jumps.

35:03.184 --> 35:06.061
He's talking to me,
but I can't hear him.

35:08.731 --> 35:10.899
Only the kiss.

35:14.195 --> 35:16.363
I never saw him again.

35:17.949 --> 35:20.617
It was the first time I ever fell in love.

35:28.876 --> 35:30.836
That's all.

35:31.045 --> 35:33.380
That was beautiful, Donna.

36:10.626 --> 36:12.252
I got him.

